# ico

**Type Property**

A type that represents Windows icon data.

## Declaration

```swift
static var ico: UTType { get }
```

## Discussion

The identifier for this type is `com.microsoft.ico`.

This type conforms to [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeImage].
